    "ELM utilizes a small number of initially hand-written programs as seeds, combining the MAP-Elites search algorithm [132] with an LLM-based intelligent mutation operation to generate a large amount of functionally rich programs as design examples.",
    "This method improves the search efficiency of GP algorithms since the LLM trained on code promote a more intelligent and effective mutation operator and reducing the probability of random mutations generating meaningless code.",
